metadata.name: Story #1: The Hollow Forest
metadata.description:
Step into the darkness of the Hollow Forest.

The Hollow Forest features in the film we are currently developing. 

Buy the NFT and join the filmmaking process as we create stories, locations and characters in the fantasy world of Vestfold and visualize the film using state of the art technology. 

NFT holders will be credited and become a patron of Vestfold.

Original visuals and text by Allan Torp Jensen.
Original music and voiceover by Paul Ewing. 

High-res film available on request.
